  # Speeding Up My Zsh Startup by 81%: From 640ms to 120ms
  
  My Zsh shell took 640ms to start. After profiling with zprof and migrating from Antigen to Zinit, I cut it down to 120ms. Here is exactly how.
  
  February 16, 2026
  
