  ## Wrapping Up [\#](https://wicksipedia.com/blog/speeding-up-zsh-startup/\#wrapping-up)
  
  Your terminal is where you spend a huge chunk of your dev time. If yours feels sluggish, donŌĆÖt guess ŌĆö profile it first. My intuition was completely wrong, and two minutes with `zprof` saved me from going down the wrong rabbit hole.
  
  **Data > Intuition.** Always.
  
