  # Little Thing \#2 ŌĆö Speeding up ZSH
  
  [![Danny Smith](https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fill:32:32/1*7kgOKJF1uKunzs4N7IV5WQ.jpeg)](https://medium.com/@dannysmith?source=post_page---byline--f1860390f92---------------------------------------)
  
